History:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
7.16.3-1: Upstream release.  ABI bump (libcurl3 -> 4).  Now uses libssh2 for
          transfers over SSH (scp:// and sftp:// URLs.)

7.15.5-1: Upstream bugfix release.

7.15.4-1: Upstream refresh.  All Cygwin-local patches have been incorporated,
          leaving a routine autoreconf as the only difference.

7.15.1-1: Upstream release.  Includes security fix for a buffer overflow,
          see <http://curl.haxx.se/docs/adv_20051207.html> for more details.

7.15.0-4: Add workaround to Curl_select() to recognise POLLHUP to fix connection
          hangs and 100% cpu usage.  (This is only necessary for cygwin1.dll
          prior to 2005-11-13.)

7.15.0-3: Initial release by new maintainer.  Please see the libcurl2 source
          package for the packaging notes of the prior maintainer.
